{"tid":1405252,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"比起丟石頭，丟雞蛋是更有效的武器，能夠有效的減緩武裝警察的攻勢","createTime":"2019-08-04T08:35:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T06:08:25.000Z","uid":66260,"like":159,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"3dcf0e75181ca72ac1ce02234672142bbe739f41","tid":1405252,"uid":66260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T08:35:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/TWSupport/photos/a.259664934154654/2329644867156640/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FTWSupport%2Fphotos%2Fa.259664934154654%2F2329644867156640%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=LFOX9O72C3pH7rxPP1PUB3vcSryOYOd41eK7VOq09cM%3D&h=9069cb31\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/TWSupport/photos/a.259664934154654/2329644867156640/?type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n<br />\n（轉發）全副武裝的抗暴警察，在獨裁國家是許多示威遊行者的惡夢，面對這樣的武裝，遊行示威的一方似乎是雞蛋碰石頭，但比起丟石頭，丟雞蛋似乎是更有效的武器。<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">雞蛋破裂後的蛋汁會黏附在頭盔及透明盾牌上，更會對防護眼鏡帶來一陣模糊</span></strong>。若再加上水球，這種抗議方式往往會更加有力。在抗議現場，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">這種蛋洗戰術，能夠有效的減緩武裝警察的攻勢，畢竟看不清楚，就很難正確的推進及抓補</span></strong>，就算抗議者被抓，雞蛋跟水球很難說的上是致命武器。<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">而且價格低廉，隨處可買，補充迅速</span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n而且雞蛋跟水，雖然對人不具殺傷力，但對這些抗暴裝備，卻是十分的難以維護，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">溫度會讓濕掉的設備發黴，雞蛋腐壞的氣味會讓配戴者難以接受。而要清潔，需要大量的人力去清洗</span></strong>，抗議就是這麼回事，增加對方的成本，維持自己抗議的能量，不讓對方贏。<br />\n<br />\n網友加碼：<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">在雞蛋面前，架設在路口的監視器也是難逃一劫</span></strong>。"},{"pid":"0ed7877e02248b9074ed76879a4c7e999a8ea931","tid":1405252,"uid":52621,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T08:38:07.000Z","msg":"好過掉磚頭 掉磚頭掉唔遠 好多時仲只係掉到石仔"},{"pid":"301ad52e9704ae328025050bb4d250846b8cb780","tid":1405252,"uid":164368,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T08:44:57.000Z","msg":"住喺我隔離有個細路，成日加啲墨汁係支水槍周圍射<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f11ee63f9a6c3809d611e3bd0556a80d6e17c66f","tid":1405252,"uid":260737,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T08:47:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.instructables.com/id/Egg-Cannon/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instructables.com%2Fid%2FEgg-Cannon%2F&d=LFOX9O72C3pH7rxPP1PUB3vcSryOYOd41eK7VOq09cM%3D&h=8e935262\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instructables.com/id/Egg-Cannon/</a>"},{"pid":"8654d8317bfd059bd05686fa5c53fe70e4628157","tid":1405252,"uid":277144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T08:48:43.000Z","msg":"光復香港"},{"pid":"2ee60896e1b6b7e88025fa9f1a4c4b9752cbe795","tid":1405252,"uid":276339,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T08:53:32.000Z","msg":"仲有番茄<br />\n番茄炒蛋好好味"},{"pid":"84c87da195479b378c3e9844c985b33ec639ad1d","tid":1405252,"uid":238275,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T08:53:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0KQLLdK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0KQLLdK.png&h=53c3a20c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"43cd42328c8a5c6fb1f45473b16cc25dd786d32b","tid":1405252,"uid":62993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T08:54:55.000Z","msg":"搵日快閃狗宿舍玩蕃茄炒蛋"},{"pid":"127efd9e420415cf8623fd36cfe5687e3d2569dd","tid":1405252,"uid":254594,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0ed7877e02248b9074ed76879a4c7e999a8ea931","tid":1405252,"uid":52621,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T08:38:07.000Z","msg":"好過掉磚頭 掉磚頭掉唔遠 好多時仲只係掉到石仔"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T08:55:10.000Z","msg":"中左其實都唔會好傷<br />\n你中一棍仲傷過佢中十舊磚"},{"pid":"208dcda57eddc345526aabf81eae379b9510ad9d","tid":1405252,"uid":29836,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T08:55:12.000Z","msg":"唔好玩食物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d213170e349d22