eplyTime":"2019-08-04T08:56:50.000Z","msg":"我想問水槍如果唔裝水 裝油嘅話<br />\n咁仲係咪叫水槍<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T08:58:38.000Z","msg":"結得濟會射唔出"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T09:02:39.000Z","msg":"咁我又有個問題<br />\n好耐無玩精靈球<br />\n扭蛋加麵粉<br />\n似唔似精靈球<br />\n一扔出去 爆開"},{"pid":"db4e04e8350d71c5473a6d4e1102e7965cb8f75f","tid":1405252,"uid":37924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T09:02:41.000Z","msg":"Why not both"},{"pid":"331d86ec844b93788097aeaf8fae5c12affcad39","tid":1405252,"uid":23373,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ba24c1259e9b9ed52683597e9261e57c80142c5a","tid":1405252,"uid":168214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"df2d3ea7666c0ff96f926ba1fa144cc9f4c057e9","tid":1405252,"uid":23373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7fb82a2916b05f23b808f9009d4980abe09638dd","tid":1405252,"uid":168214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T08:56:50.000Z","msg":"我想問水槍如果唔裝水 裝油嘅話<br />\n咁仲係咪叫水槍<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T08:58:38.000Z","msg":"結得濟會射唔出"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T09:02:39.000Z","msg":"咁我又有個問題<br />\n好耐無玩精靈球<br />\n扭蛋加麵粉<br />\n似唔似精靈球<br />\n一扔出去 爆開"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T09:06:30.000Z","msg":"你落樓下試下最遠可以掟幾遠先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n多數大家最多掟到10-20米最盡<br />\n<br />\n而同警犬條防線，好多時都4-50米<br />\n<br />\n同埋扭蛋殼比你想像中硬淨，唔係落地基本上唔會爛<br />\n<br />\n掟人掟頭都唔多會爛"},{"pid":"6f8a16625852b7cd5df2a2345f4375d850c99d77","tid":1405252,"uid":285536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T09:10:33.000Z","msg":"不要說「黑警，可恥」, 試著說「黑社會」<br />\n不要說「香港警察，知法犯法」<br />\n試著說「不畏懼、不徇私、不對他人懷惡意」<br />\n終極核彈級口號, 有機會造成永久心理創傷, 相信好快用得<br />\n「殺人兇手」"},{"pid":"24